    <h2>🔴 Priority 1: A.2 K8s Readiness - Phase 1 (4-5 hours)</h2>
    
    <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #ff6b6b; margin: 15px 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #d9534f; margin-top: 0;">URGENT: This is the critical blocker for K8s migration</h3>
        <p><strong>Master Plan Reference:</strong> A.2 in Priority Matrix - CRITICAL importance, HIGH effort, STRATEGIC initiative</p>
    </div>

    <h3>Task: Create A.2 Requirements Specification</h3>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Gather K8s Environment Prerequisites:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Research: What are Comserv's minimum K8s version requirements?</li>
                <li>Document: Required cluster size, node resources (CPU/memory), storage (persistent volumes)</li>
                <li>List: Required K8s add-ons (ingress controller, storage provisioner, monitoring)</li>
                <li>Identify: Load balancing strategy (service type, external LB)</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Application Readiness Assessment:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Audit: Docker image structure (Is current Dockerfile K8s-ready?)</li>
                <li>Check: Health checks configured (liveness/readiness probes)</li>
                <li>Review: Environment variable usage (injectable via ConfigMap/Secrets)</li>
                <li>Verify: Database connection strategy for stateless pods</li>
                <li>Confirm: Volume requirements for persistent data</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Create Draft Specification Document:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Write: /Documentation/A2_Kubernetes_Readiness_Specification.tt</li>
                <li>Sections: Overview, K8s Requirements, Application Changes Needed, Migration Timeline</li>
                <li>Format: Use documentation_tt_template.tt as base</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ol>
    <p><strong>Expected Deliverable:</strong> A.2 Requirements Specification (500+ words) with clear list of prerequisites and application changes needed</p>
    <p><strong>Time Estimate:</strong> 4-5 hours | <strong>Success Criteria:</strong> Document complete + dependencies identified</p>

    <h2>🟠 Priority 2: E.1 Phase 3 Completion Validation (1-1.5 hours)</h2>
    
    <h3>Task: End-to-End AI Chat Widget Testing</h3>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Verify Widget UI/UX from Dec 31 work:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Access application at http://localhost:5000</li>
                <li>Hard refresh browser (Ctrl+Shift+R)</li>
                <li>Check: "Chat with AI" button visible and styled correctly</li>
                <li>Test: Open/close chat panel smoothly</li>
                <li>Test: Type message and submit</li>
                <li>Verify: Response displays with proper formatting</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Validate Database Recording:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Connect to MariaDB console</li>
                <li>Query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM ai_conversations; (should be > 0)</li>
                <li>Query: SELECT * FROM ai_messages LIMIT 5; (verify message storage)</li>
                <li>Check: Timestamps are current (not null)</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Document Final Status:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Create: /Documentation/E1_Phase3_Completion_Report.tt</li>
                <li>Include: What works ✅, what needs fixing ❌, any blockers for Phase 4</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ol>
    <p><strong>Expected Deliverable:</strong> E.1 Phase 3 Completion Report + verified working widget</p>
    <p><strong>Time Estimate:</strong> 1-1.5 hours | <strong>Success Criteria:</strong> Widget functional, DB recording verified, report complete</p>

    <h2>🟡 Priority 3: A.3 Credentials Audit - Scope Planning (30 min)</h2>
    
    <h3>Task: Define Audit Scope and Schedule</h3>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Create A.3 Credentials Audit Plan:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>List all credential types: API keys, SSH keys, DB passwords, OAuth tokens, TLS certs</li>
                <li>Identify: Where stored currently (code, env vars, secrets manager, .env files)</li>
                <li>Flag: Which are hardcoded/insecure</li>
                <li>Plan: Migration to secure secrets management (Docker Secrets, K8s Secrets)</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li><strong>Write: A.3 Audit Scope Document</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>File: /Documentation/A3_Credentials_Audit_Plan.tt</li>
                <li>Sections: Current State, Issues Found, Remediation Plan, Timeline</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ol>
    <p><strong>Expected Deliverable:</strong> A.3 Audit Scope Document (preliminary, will be expanded Jan 4-5)</p>
    <p><strong>Time Estimate:</strong> 30 minutes</p>

